HEADWORD: Bondmaid
<hw>Bond"maid`</hw> <pr>(-m⟦amac⟧d`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Bond</ets>, <pos>a.</pos> or <pos>n.</pos> +
<ets>maid</ets>.]</ety> <def>A female slave, or one bound to service
without wages, as distinguished from a hired servant.</def>⟦br⟧
